The paper deals with the simulation of human collective behavior, which is a topic that falls under computer graphics (cs.GR) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The study also involves image and video processing (cs.CV), social and information networks (cs.SI), and multimedia (cs.MM) as it uses visual stimuli to test human perception.
